{"tid":1914632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[針拮麻包袋] 原來查飛狗係真 狗 黎！","createTime":"2020-03-07T16:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T16:28:48.000Z","uid":154486,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9750805c9e32d551bebe94b712b86d75b559f877","tid":1914632,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:10:33.000Z","msg":"資料顯示，顧客服務及收益保護隊（內部簡稱CSRPU）於2019年1月1日成立，隸屬於港鐵收益事務部，主要負責打擊逃票及濫用乘車優惠、事故處理、人群管制、鐵路處所內的公眾活動及協助身體不適的乘客等等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CSRPU共設有10個小隊，每隊由1個隊長和3至4個隊員組成，部份成員為現任輔警。</span></span></strong>他們均穿著與現時港鐵車務員工標準黃色制服，亦會因行動需要，派出便裝人員配合行動。<br />\n<br />\n查完飛收工happy下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157d90b9b289913de144439ae0e43e221022918b","tid":1914632,"uid":154486,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n從今以後<br />\n查飛狗當真狗"},{"pid":"0d023f5f58e09c15bb17ff6933608b2357904f35","tid":1914632,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"負皮果個解釋下"},{"pid":"db69d7a539ceae5102cf2fd78d68aefc6fe322e9","tid":1914632,"uid":213793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:12:54.000Z","msg":"醬油？"},{"pid":"a6ff5cbe75693eebd654dc4ea7701ae64a8d5102","tid":1914632,"uid":115040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95c3d2cbd0e641a22207bb718c8d51deeea714b0","tid":1914632,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"204b30fa0f6b2bf63e348126019b28ca9810ca37","tid":1914632,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要尊重查飛sir既辛勞"},{"pid":"9d005c1a30d4400c24ec0a4dd4f0d316b2967de4","tid":1914632,"uid":230141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score